ol</em> 2007;118(1):108–110.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijcard.2006.05.075">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16891017/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Coronary+artery+dissection+after+blunt+chest+trauma%3A+depiction+at+multidetector-row+computed+tomography&amp;author=Y+Sato&amp;author=N+Matsumoto&amp;author=S+Komatsu&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Int+J+Cardiol&amp;pages=108-110&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.ijcard.2006.05.075&amp;pmid=16891017">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">67.</div><div id="r67" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Sheikh M, Ben-Nakhi A, Shukkur AM, Sinan T, Al-Rashdan I. Accuracy of 64-multidetector-row computed tomography in the diagnosis of coronary artery disease. <em>Med Princ Pract</em> 2009;18(4):323–328.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1159/000215732">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19494542/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Accuracy+of+64-multidetector-row+computed+tomography+in+the+diagnosis+of+coronary+artery+disease&amp;author=M+Sheikh&amp;author=A+Ben-Nakhi&amp;author=AM+Shukkur&amp;author=T+Sinan&amp;author=I+Al-Rashdan&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=Med+Princ+Pract&amp;pages=323-328&amp;doi=10.1159%2F000215732&amp;pmid=19494542">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">68.</div><div id="r68" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kan CD, Yang YJ. Traumatic aortic and mitral valve injury following blunt chest injury with a var